.TH JTUTIL-LOG2BIN "1" "April 2026" "jtutil-log2bin manual" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jtutil-log2bin \- Convert MAME debug.log output to binary
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate the input file with the wpset command of the MAME debugger.
Use \fB\-a0\fR and \fB\-s\fR to specify the beginning of the region and its size.
The binary file produced can the be loaded into jtframe_ram modules.
.PP
Run this command several times to parse different regions.
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
jtutil log2bin [flags]
.SS "Flags:"
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
help for log2bin
.TP
\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR string
name of output file (default "debug.bin")
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-size\fR int
region length (default 1024)
.TP
\fB\-a\fR, \fB\-\-start\fR int
address start of region
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
verbose
